race.comment: LORD AKOMEED (2) proved too strong two runs ago at this track. Safely held last time out when ninth over 1000m at Kempsey. Well placed to take this out. HOMELAND (8) accounted for a maiden field over 1000m at Bowraville last start. Re-unites with Raymond Spokes who was on board last start. Capable of taking the next step. SURCOTE (6) was out of the money two runs back then again missed the frame last start when ninth over 1200m at the Gold Coast Poly. Has the talent to test these. RAISED BY WOLVES (7) is back after a break of six months. Started the last campaign impressively when in the placings over 1012m at this track. Among the better hopes.
